            "description": "<p>A spinning metal pole covered in deadly blades is hidden in the ceiling, connected to several trigger plates around the room and a hidden control panel built into the bed frame.</p>",
            "disable": "<p>@Check[thievery|dc:39] (master) three times on a pillar, or @Check[thievery|dc:37] (master) twice on the control panel deactivates the whole trap. Breaking the control panel prevents anyone from disabling the trap using the control panel and prevents the trap from deactivating automatically (see Reset below)</p>",
